This suggests that the paper is likely to fall under the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. Additionally, the paper may also fall under programming languages (cs.PL) as it discusses the use of functions as the primitive unit of composition. The investigation of graph measures also suggests that the paper may fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or systems and control (cs.SD) sub-categories.
